{"tid":657134,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"聚利寶8527 僅超額認購9.8倍","createTime":"2018-05-08T00:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T03:31:25.000Z","uid":110740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1af1a9af8e157184ef8b2aab6e6fab5c694085","tid":657134,"uid":110740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:28:12.000Z","msg":"餐飲集團聚利寶控股(08527)公布招股結果，發售價定為0.5港元，每股招股價介乎0.5至0.6元；淨籌2,370萬元，認購1手(5,000股)中籤率70%，申請18手(即9萬股)始穩獲一手。股份將於明日(9日)於創業板上市。 <br />\n<br />\n是次公開發售股份錄得約9.8倍超額認購，公開發售股份維持於1,250萬股；而配售項下初步提呈發售的配售股份已獲適度超額認購。 <br />\n<br />\n該公司在新加坡共擁有8間餐廳(其中6間以Central Hong Kong Caf&eacute;」品牌營運、1間以「Black Society」品牌營運，另外1間以特許營運「Greyhound Caf&eacute;」品牌營運。在馬來西亞則以「Bread Story」品牌營運20間烘焙零售店。 <br />\n<br />\nFatfat了 無回撥 下限定價 今次仲唔Fatfat？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1023cae394d9cdcf85691f9d40db8a37725a1b9e","tid":657134,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:29:02.000Z","msg":"正呀"},{"pid":"6fa234b91276dcf56678605d20c31cdd3010d91b","tid":657134,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"上下限定價係點計？"},{"pid":"047c38ddaa1e92d960fe128f8901754b6b3cdb23","tid":657134,"uid":13420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無回撥"},{"pid":"acb1472442c0c16c3467cfd5e29413adfaecef91","tid":657134,"uid":52684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"無人講？我暗盤掃貨先"},{"pid":"175be0265f1b963b26519d37728401840e53f8aa","tid":657134,"uid":181750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload